            <div class="pb-agent-detail-box" id="wf7-rec"><h4>Part 1 -- Reconciliation</h4><div class="pb-agent-spec-grid"><div class="pb-agent-spec-block"><h5>Match Logic</h5><ul><li>Match payment to invoice by PO reference or customer + amount</li><li>Exact amount match &rarr; mark PAID in Sheet</li><li>Amount variance &lt;5% &rarr; PARTIAL flag, alert AR manager</li><li>Amount variance &gt;5% &rarr; MISMATCH, alert, do not close invoice</li><li>No invoice match &rarr; UNMATCHED, alert immediately</li></ul></div><div class="pb-agent-spec-block"><h5>Hard Rules</h5><ul><li>Never mark invoice paid without exact amount match (or override)</li><li>Payment dispute webhook &rarr; pause dunning for account, alert</li><li>Duplicate payment detected &rarr; hard stop, alert AR manager</li></ul></div></div></div>

            <div class="pb-agent-detail-box" id="wf7-age"><h4>Part 2 -- Aging + DSO</h4><div class="pb-agent-spec-grid"><div class="pb-agent-spec-block"><h5>Aging Buckets</h5><ul><li>Current (not yet due)</li><li>1-30 days past due</li><li>31-60 days past due</li><li>61-90 days past due</li><li>90+ days past due</li></ul></div><div class="pb-agent-spec-block"><h5>DSO Formula</h5><ul><li>Rolling 90-day: (Total AR / Revenue last 90 days) x 90</li><li>Week-over-week trend calculated (improving / worsening / flat)</li><li>DSO &gt;45 days &rarr; Slack ping to CFO (awareness only)</li></ul></div></div></div>

